reviewText:
Hulk Hogan Real American (WS901)
07/30/88 Hulk Hogan vs. Andre the Giant (steel cage match)
10/03/85 Hulk Hogan vs. Nikolai Volkoff (flag match)
10/25/88 Hulk Hogan vs. King Haku
11/87 Hulk Hogan vs. Ted DiBiase
This is a great video for any Hogan fan.  Hogan vs Andre in a steel cage, Hogan vs Nikolai Volkoff, King Haku and the Million Dollar Man make this video a definite must see.
